      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/587024505_18539218915018992_4622657388731799348_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc4NTkyNTE0NzcwMjYyNTc3MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQzMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=a8Eb64Y0BcMQ7kNvwGL7vpQ&amp;_nc_oc=AdrLNhfaoRaVh1Vx0pwPl9sycHAujb-10ZakofRQw1LpqrkyKeIdHtySofXBDmDLUOo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DvD3LNMY546fSEihbj2vpA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyC7x8J4_bkW6bCGbZ0jfv3wc0qo_tttXbsRkgsdwG47w&amp;oe=69C8E761" alt="Instagram billede fra @evrentekinoktay" /></p><p><strong>@evrentekinoktay</strong></p><p>Thank you to everyone who has already visited my exhibition Boogie. It will run for one more month and its final day is January 11.<br/>
<br/>
Once again, many thanks to @nikolajkunsthal — and especially to @helenenyborgbay for giving me the opportunity to exhibit— something that felt like an utopian dream when I was a very young artist.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/587024505_18539218915018992_4622657388731799348_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc4NTkyNTE0NzcwMjYyNTc3MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQzMy5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=a8Eb64Y0BcMQ7kNvwGL7vpQ&amp;_nc_oc=AdrLNhfaoRaVh1Vx0pwPl9sycHAujb-10ZakofRQw1LpqrkyKeIdHtySofXBDmDLUOo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DvD3LNMY546fSEihbj2vpA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyC7x8J4_bkW6bCGbZ0jfv3wc0qo_tttXbsRkgsdwG47w&amp;oe=69C8E761" alt="Instagram billede fra @evrentekinoktay" /></p><p><strong>@evrentekinoktay</strong></p><p>Thank you to everyone who has already visited my exhibition Boogie. It will run for one more month and its final day is January 11.<br/>
<br/>
Once again, many thanks to @nikolajkunsthal — and especially to @helenenyborgbay for giving me the opportunity to exhibit— something that felt like an utopian dream when I was a very young artist.</p>]]></content:encoded>
